import './App.css';
import Right from './components/Right'
import Choose from './components/Choose'
import Addemployee from './components/Addemployee'
import Search from './components/Search'
import Searchall from './components/Searchall'
import Broadcast from './components/Broadcast'
import Project from './components/Project'
import Attendance from './components/Attendance'
import TandC from './components/TandC'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route , Routes} from "react-router-dom";

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
        <Routes>
        <Route exact path="/" element={<Right />} />
        <Route exact path="Employee" element={<Choose />} />
          <Route exact path="Broadcast" element={<Broadcast />} />
          <Route exact path="Projects" element={<Project />} />
          <Route exact path="Attendance" element={<Attendance />} />
          <Route exact path="Terms and Conditions" element={<TandC />} />
          <Route exact path="Addemployee" element={<Addemployee name={"Add New Admin"}/>} />
          <Route exact path="Search" element={<Search name={'Search Admin'}/>} />
          <Route exact path="Searchall" element={<Searchall name={'Show All Admin'}/>} />
          <Route exact path="Addemployee1" element={<Addemployee name={"Add New Employee"}/>} />
          <Route exact path="Search1" element={<Search name={'Search Employee'}/>} />
          <Route exact path="Searchall1" element={<Searchall name={'Show All Employee'}/>} />
        </Routes>
      </Router>
    </>
  );
}

export default App;
